Package: powerlog
Type: Package
Title: power and sample size calculation for logistic regression
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Zora Yezi Yang
Maintainer: The package maintainer <zora@zorayang.com>
Description: Calculate power and sample size based on a range of hypothesized effect sizes.
    Support univariate calculations for normal, uniform, t-distributed and binary data.
    Allow single adjustment variable assuming a bi-variate normal structure.
    Upload design matrix for univariate and bivariate regressions using an empirical data distribution.
